latestIgtvVideos.title: 5 ways to wear your one black denim.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
So here’s the five different ways how you can style your one black denim. Either you going for casual outing or party or going for cute look or you want to dress up like a tomboy you can literally play with your one piece of denim and can create magic. 
I was always fascinated to dress up different every single day but because of the budget and other things I couldn’t buy so many clothes so I always love to play with whatever I have in my wardrobe and try to create new Outfit every day. 
So that’s why I am starting the series called PLAY WITH IT in which I am going to show you that how you can use one piece of cloth from your wardrobe in a different ways so that you have something new to wear every day. .
